  "instructions": [
    "Heat the tava griddle over medium heat and drizzle sesame oil.",
    "Add the sliced sausage and cook until lightly browned.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and grated ginger, cooking for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add shredded cabbage and julienned carrot, sautéing until the vegetables are crisp-tender.",
    "Pour in the fry-grind rice and stir-fry for 3 minutes to heat through.",
    "Splash in low-sodium soy sauce and season with salt and pepper.",
    "Fold in sliced spring onions and chopped dill, cooking for an additional minute.",
    "Remove from heat and serve hot straight from the griddle."
